title: Variety Pack - Ready-to-Blend Smoothies Order ships & arrives separately from meals. | On-The-Go Goodness
description: Whether you have one for breakfast, a post-workout boost, or a quick snack, our ready-to-blend smoothies are just what you need! This assortment features one of each of our flavors, including Peachy Mango, Banana Berry, Acai-Cherry Berry, Cocoa Banana Nut, and Tropical Greens—plus a bonus Banana Berry. To enjoy one of these fruit-packed, no-sugar-added blends, all you have to do is blend them with the liquid of your choice (we like milk) until smooth and enjoy!

*To ensure the highest quality when you receive your smoothies, they will come in a separate box from your meals. Your Ready-to-Blend Smoothie box may arrive a few days after your meal box. Smoothies should be stored frozen.

