1 unit Peachy Mango Ready-to-Blend Smoothie
2 unit Banana Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie
1 unit Acai-Cherry Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie
1 unit Cocoa Banana Nut Ready-to-Blend Smoothie
1 unit Tropical Greens Ready-to-Blend Smoothie

Fill a cup with liquid of your choice (we recommend milk or water).

Pour contents into blender; blend until smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!